  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8582039">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8582039/" class="title-link">入门好书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8582039"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/huangbobooo/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u132350870-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/huangbobooo/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">忆往昔</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-06-04"
      class="main-meta">2017-06-04 21:21:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8582039_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  九十年代间的文章合集，现在看来仍不过时，很有预见性，一本居安思危的好书，没有晦涩难懂的术语和理论，阅读困难不大。它所分析和预见的社会现象现在都有出现——长期和平以及和平自身的问题，民主的限制，国际关系等，作者对和平与民主做了另一种诠释，开拓了新视野。书主要...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
