  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8296767/" class="title-link">对于未来社会的杂篇</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8296767"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/celia_xy/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49621195-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/celia_xy/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">惜遥</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-01-17"
      class="main-meta">2017-01-17 01:43:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8296767_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一开始读这本书，纯粹是被书名带歪的。“无政府时代”活生生被念成了“无政府主义”，我也不知道是不是网络时代的降临，微信的频繁使用，导致连一个书名，都没法好好完整的读了。总之，不看各种简介就开始读书的我，就这么被坑进去了。  也没期待是本多么好读的书，无政府时代...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
